### **GLOBAL Memory (Cross-State)**
**What to store:**
- Overall prompt philosophy (concise vs. comprehensive)
- Audience they target (technical vs. general)
- Output format preferences (bullet points vs. prose)
- Quality bar (perfectionist vs. pragmatic)

**Influences ALL states:**
